llowing{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brandonroberts/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2026-03-02T17:27:44Z","updated_at":"2026-03-03T13:55:59Z","closed_at":"2026-03-03T13:55:59Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Great work on this project!\n\nUpon trying it on a separate Angular project, I noticed the `@angular/compiler` import being used in the `main.ts`. This shouldn't be needed if the code is AOT compiled, along with the Angular packages being linked. There is a linker plugin but it seems to be skipping over the Angular packages that aren't linked by the rolldown dep optimization plugin.\n\nThe plugin below fixes the issue by adding it to the vite.config.ts, but this should be able to be fixed internally in this package.\n\n```ts\nimport type { Plugin } from 'vite';\nimport { JavaScriptTransformer } from '@angular/build/private';\n\nexport function depsPlugin(): Plugin {\n  const javascriptTransformer = new JavaScriptTransformer({ jit: true, sourcemap: true }, 1);\n\n  /**\n   * Transforms Angular packages the didn't get picked up by Vite's pre-optimization.\n   */\n  return {\n    name: 'deps-optimization',\n    enforce: 'pre',\n    transform: {\n      filter: {\n        code: /from \"\\.\\/core-/,\n      },\n      async handler(_code: string, id: string) {\n        const path = id.split('?')[0];\n        const contents = await javascriptTransformer.transformFile(path);\n        console.log(id);\n        return {\n          code: Buffer.from(contents).toString('utf-8'),\n        };\n      },\n    },\n  };\n}\n```\n\nWe do something similar in the AnalogJS Vite plugin also \nhttps://github.com/analogjs/analog/blob/beta/packages/vite-plugin-angular/src/lib/router-plugin.ts\n\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/voidzero-dev/oxc-angular-compiler/issues/46/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/voidzero-dev/oxc-angular-compiler/issues/46/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2084","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2084/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2084/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2084/events","html_url":"https://github.com/analogjs/analog/issues/2084","id":3982322857,"node_id":"I_kwDOHnhHGM7tXWyp","number":2084,"title":"Fresh project not working on Windows 11","user":{"login":"konuch","id":6041136,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYwNDExMzY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6041136?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konuch","html_url":"https://github.com/konuch","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konuch/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konuch/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konuch/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://ap