//api.github.com/repos/ericfitz/tmi-ux/milestones/4","html_url":"https://github.com/ericfitz/tmi-ux/milestone/4","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ericfitz/tmi-ux/milestones/4/labels","id":14855844,"node_id":"MI_kwDOOVIo5M4A4q6k","number":4,"title":"1.3.0","description":null,"creator":{"login":"ericfitz","id":2677124,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2NzcxMjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2677124?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz","html_url":"https://github.com/ericfitz","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ericfitz/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":79,"state":"closed","created_at":"2026-02-18T15:28:21Z","updated_at":"2026-03-23T01:21:58Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":"2026-03-23T01:21:58Z"},"comments":3,"created_at":"2025-11-24T21:39:39Z","updated_at":"2026-03-23T01:21:03Z","closed_at":"2026-02-20T17:31:25Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":2,"completed":2,"percent_completed":100},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Overview\n\nTrack the migration from Angular 20.x to Angular 21. This migration is currently blocked by dependency compatibility issues.\n\n## Current Status\n\n**Blocked** - Cannot upgrade until dependencies are ready\n\n### Current Versions (as of January 2026)\n- Angular Core: 20.3.15\n- Angular CLI: 20.3.12\n- Angular Material: 20.2.14\n- Angular CDK: 20.2.14\n- AnalogJS: 1.22.5\n- ngx-markdown: 20.1.0\n- zone.js: 0.15.1\n\n### Target Versions\n- Angular Core: 21.0.x\n- Angular CLI: 21.0.x\n- Angular Material: 21.0.x\n- Angular CDK: 21.0.x\n- AnalogJS: 2.x (stable, with Angular 21 support)\n- ngx-markdown: 21.x\n- zone.js: 0.16.x\n\n## Blockers\n\n### 1. AnalogJS v2.x - **Primary Blocker**\n\n**Status:** Still in beta (v2.0.0-beta.22 as of January 2026)\n\n**Details:**\n- Current beta peer dependencies only support Angular 15-20\n- No stable v2.x release yet\n- Angular 21 support not yet declared in peer dependencies\n\n**Monitor:** https://github.com/analogjs/analog/releases\n\n**Condition to proceed:** AnalogJS v2.x stable release with `@angular-devkit/build-angular@^21.0.0` in peer dependencies\n\n### 2. ngx-markdown v21 - **Secondary Blocker**\n\n**Status:** Not released\n\n**Details:**\n- Current latest: v20.1.0\n- Peer dependency requires Angular 20.x: `@angular/core@^20.0.0`\n- No v21 release or beta available\n\n**Monitor:** https://github.com/jfcere/ngx-markdown/releases\n\n**Condition to proceed:** ngx-markdown v21.x release with Angular 21 peer dependency support\n\n### 3. zone.js 0.16.x\n\n**Status:** Available but dependent on Angular 21\n\n**Details:**\n- zone.js 0.16.0 is available and designed for Angular 21\n- Should be upgraded as part of Angular 21 migration\n- Not a blocker, but a coordinated upgrade\n\n## Impact - What This Unblocks\n\nWhen Angular 21 migration is complete, we will be able to:\n\n1. **Upgrade zone.js** to 0.16.x (Angular 21's default)\n2. **Upgrade marked** to v17.x (see issue #263 - blocked by ngx-markdown peer dep)\n3. **Access Angular 21 features:**\n   - Zoneless change detection (experimental → stable)\n   - Signal Forms improvements\n   - Enhanced performance optimizations\n   - Updated Angular DevTools\n4. **Update angular-eslint** to v21 with new linting rules\n5. **Resolve Dependabot PRs** that are currently blocked\n\n## What to Monitor\n\n- [ ] **AnalogJS releases:** Watch for v2.0.0 stable with Angular 21 support\n  - https://github.com/analogjs/analog/releases\n  - Check peer dependencies include `@angular-devkit/build-angular@^21.0.0`\n- [ ] **ngx-markdown releases:** Watch for v21.x\n  - https://github.com/jfcere/ngx-markdown/releases\n- [ ] **Angular 21 ecosystem stability:** Community feedback on production readiness\n- [ ] **Third-party library compatibility:** Ensure other deps are Angular 21 compatible\n\n## Migration Steps (when ready)\n\n### Prerequisites Checklist\n- [ ] AnalogJS v2.x stable with Angular 21 support\n- [ ] ngx-markdown v21.x available\n- [ ] All other third-party libraries compatible\n\n### Migration Process\n\n1. **Update all Angular packages simultaneously:**\n   ```bash\n   pnpm add @angular/animations@^21 @angular/common@^21 @angular/compiler@^21 @angular/core@^21 @angular/forms@^21 @angular/platform-browser@^21 @angular/platform-browser-dynamic@^21 @angular/router@^21 @angular/cdk@^21 @angular/material@^21 zone.js@^0.16\n   pnpm add -D @angular/cli@^21 @angular/compiler-cli@^21 @angular-devkit/build-angular@^21\n   pnpm add -D @angular-eslint/builder@^21 @angular-eslint/eslint-plugin@^21 @angular-eslint/eslint-plugin-template@^21 @angular-eslint/schematics@^21 @angular-eslint/template-parser@^21 angular-eslint@^21\n   ```\n\n2. **Update AnalogJS:**\n   ```bash\n   pnpm add -D @analogjs/vite-plugin-angular@^2\n   ```\n\n3. **Update ngx-markdown:**\n   ```bash\n   pnpm add ngx-markdown@^21\n   ```\n\n4. **Run Angular migrations:**\n   ```bash\n   ng update @angular/core@21 @angular/cli@21\n   ```\n\n5. **Test thoroughly:**\n   ```bash\n   pnpm run lint:all\n   pnpm run build\n   pnpm test\n   pnpm run test:e2e\n   ```\n\n6. **After Angular 21 is stable, update marked** (see issue #263)\n\n## Related Issues and PRs\n\n- Issue #263: marked v17 upgrade (blocked by ngx-markdown peer dep)\n- Various Dependabot PRs for Angular 21 packages (closed as premature)\n\n## References\n\n- [Angular v21 Release](https://angular.dev/events/v21)\n- [AnalogJS Compatibility](https://analogjs.org/docs/guides/compatibility)\n- [ngx-markdown Releases](https://github.com/jfcere/ngx-markdown/releases)","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ericfitz/tmi-ux/issues/241/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ericfitz/tmi-ux/issues/241/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2097","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2097/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2097/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/analogjs/analog/issues/2097/events","html_url":"https://github.com/analogjs/analog/issues/2097","id":4011667944,"node_id":"I_kwDOHnhHGM7vHTHo","number":2097,"title":"[vitest-angular]: NG0304: 'search' is not a known element","user":{"login":"jase88","id":804836,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjgwNDgzNg==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/804836?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88","html_url":"https://github.com/jase88","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase88/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jase